{"tid":1550012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北區告急","createTime":"2019-09-07T13:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T12:04:43.000Z","uid":318152,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"486aafe88e011f839404d46b2ee9a69da5da2843","tid":1550012,"uid":318152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"三個月以來，政府一直忽視民間五大訴求。<br />\n近日林鄭提出撤回條例，但是事件仍有變數。而林鄭繼續包庇警察濫權濫捕，過份使用武力，使用不合理方式對待示威者，不願成立獨立調查委員會，繼續與民意背道而馳，民怨有增無減。<br />\n<br />\n九月九日<br />\n<br />\n田家炳&times;風采&times;上官，三所圍繞著清河邨的中學，三間學校的關注組決定在百和路上組成人鏈，表達對政府的不滿，敦促政府回應五大訴求。同時，希望校方正視問題，不要避談政治，尊重校內不同聲音，同時成立校內平台讓在校生發聲。<br />\n<br />\n0725集合<br />\n0740拉手<br />\n0810解散<br />\n<br />\n上官集合：清河邨轉角位<br />\n田家炳集合：田家炳中學<br />\n風采集合：清河邨ok<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各畢業舊生，在校學生以及街坊參與。<br />\n服飾：不限 可戴口罩<br />\n（以上言論不代表學校立場）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ROHCJkP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FROHCJkP.jpg&h=726b3a40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/07/215340_3017d17c5e6744a8911efb5049da36c4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F07%2F215340_3017d17c5e6744a8911efb5049da36c4.jpeg&h=d47997e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebb02d0f6b048fed549a080f64342ccd1dc30c72","tid":1550012,"uid":308423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:55:18.000Z","msg":"北區人推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ee2c5003a63b12ba04f3c7cc1a44c86a4653ab","tid":1550012,"uid":260614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:56:53.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"b336a43212a39697e5a2dec340ee0ae889562c44","tid":1550012,"uid":260614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:57:09.000Z","msg":"北區人做嘢啊"},{"pid":"ffd180256f01822b11d2b28273f857c24a2b3669","tid":1550012,"uid":260614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:57:38.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁啊"},{"pid":"9f844ba10955d5f8a3dd8635aac689ce4b1de160","tid":1550012,"uid":285854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:58:49.000Z","msg":"北區人推"},{"pid":"7387caa3760b82fcad5a2d8f177a1c8d7a9e1b9d","tid":1550012,"uid":318152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"推爆佢 唔好比大陸人入侵！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b33b32758a9a42b109c9684c91808fbd90aee72","tid":1550012,"uid":262466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:00:02.000Z","msg":"p牌冇得推都要推一推"},{"pid":"f56adcaae1e8bd8afafe3b9bb0c4c08243dbbe70","tid":1550012,"uid":260614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"update<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Cmsk9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Cmsk9Z.jpg&h=59cdbd06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1aaec7c94e45b669b20858c436be0d64d5c89b5d","tid":1550012,"uid":260614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:01:37.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"40fc3ea05f1f5237399f44ef547a50fb203d6cd5","tid":1550012,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:02:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1d31e2a46d94f9f2ea58cdaabfd5e7df99298a8","tid":1550012,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>九月八，遮打見！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZUq8PfJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUq8PfJ.png&h=6ed8457a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><ins><span style=\"color: purple;\">最好2點半前到達簽署！</span></ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k5RDr3G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk5RDr3G.jpg&h=fc849298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">記定英文口號</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mq23Dbz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMq23Dbz.png&h=28cc984b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8azEVYe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8azEVYe.png&h=f85b965a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W8g0FpV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW8g0FpV.png&h=b3716331&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">最後唔好意思阻多你十分鐘睇睇人權法其實係咩黎</span></strong><img src=\"/as